&lt;p&gt;Please note that we &lt;strong&gt;do not&lt;/strong&gt; charge admission for Ultra Light Startups events in Boston but you must reserve an Eventbrite ticket at the link below because&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;the venue will reach capacity!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
